    "story_text": "Loto Fabrics began in Dubai in 2019, with a bolt of silk and a single zardozi artisan. Today our studio in Al Quoz produces bridal and occasion cloth for clients in 14 countries. We sell by the meter because cloth this rare deserves to be measured, not packaged.",
